{"type":"message","id":"decc2061","parentId":"ba91e39e","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:21:45.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在我有了 2 篇笔记。让我继续进行阶段二：自检与应用。\n\n## 阶段二：自检与应用（8分钟）\n\n### 第四步：自检 - 任务状态","thinkingSignature":"ac35bf21863ec49f62faceee1bb524d33ee861f93c8e1d9ff9d51ad5340f2646"},{"type":"text","text":"## 阶段二：自检与应用（8分钟）\n\n### 第四步：自检 - 任务状态\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g6xrx6gypgv5_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":19080,"output":104,"cacheRead":36342,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55526,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773843702012}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec5c9e95","parentId":"decc2061","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:21:45.297Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_g6xrx6gypgv5_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5cab973e-d17e-41d2-b5c3-419ba9651915\",\n      \"agentId\": \"guan-guan\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:guan-guan:session-1773754048809\",\n      \"name\": \"管管进化心跳 - 每20分钟\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773817720694,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773843558605,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/20 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【第 N 轮进化心跳 - 升级版】\\n\\n执行20分钟进化轮次，包含学习和应用两个阶段：\\n\\n## 阶段一：学习（10分钟）\\n\\n### 第一步：搜索 (3分钟)\\n- 使用 web_search 搜索 AI Agent 相关最新信息\\n- 搜索 5-10 个不同来源\\n- 如果搜索不可用，直接抓取 Anthropic 工程博客\\n\\n### 第二步：阅读提取 (3分钟)\\n- 使用 web_fetch 读取有价值的内容\\n- 提取 1-2 个核心要点\\n\\n### 第三步：写作产出 (4分钟)\\n- 将提取的内容写成笔记，保存到 knowledge/ 对应目录\\n- 如果有可复用的框架，提取为模板\\n- 如果有实战经验，整理为案例\\n\\n## 阶段二：自检与应用（8分钟）\\n\\n### 第四步：自检 - 任务状态（3分钟）\\n- 调用 cron list 查看当前所有任务状态\\n- 标记任何出错的任务（lastRunStatus=error）\\n- 标记任何连续错误（consecutiveErrors>0）\\n- 标记任何即将超时或异常的任务\\n\\n### 第五步：应用 - 修复与优化（4分钟）\\n根据学到的知识，尝试修复问题：\\n- 如果发现出错的任务，尝试分析错误原因\\n- 用今天学的知识优化工作流\\n- 如果是简单问题，直接修复；复杂问题记录到待办\\n\\n### 第六步：反思（1分钟）\\n- 读取当前的 evolution-plan.md\\n- 记录本轮发现的问题和修复情况\\n- 思考如何进一步优化\\n\\n## 产出汇报\\n完成后输出：\\n- 本轮新增笔记: X 篇\\n- 本轮新增模板: X 个\\n- 本轮新增案例: X 个\\n- 自检发现问题: X 个\\n- 已修复问题: X 个\\n- 方案优化点: XXX\\n\\n开始执行！\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 1200\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773843600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773843410507,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 148098,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1773843600007\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"58b564ba-7837-434a-9d8e-632542b6443d\",\n      \"agentId\": \"xiao-yi\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:xiao-yi:main\",\n      \"name\": \"小艺感知心跳 - 每15分钟\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773837490104,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773843323748,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/15 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"请执行 perception.py 脚本并输出感知报告。脚本路径: C:\\\\Users\\\\16343\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\xiao-yi\\\\workspace\\\\perception.py\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 60\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773844200000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773843300012,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 23736,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 10min\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773744532964,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773840793748,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"everyMs\": 600000,\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773840694145\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run EvoMap heartbeat. Execute: uv run python guan_guan_publish.py in C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\16343\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace. Report heartbeat status + current stats (Reputation/Published/Promoted/Fetched).\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773844393748,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773840768740,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 25008,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 6,\n        \"lastError\": \"AxiosError: Request failed with status code 400\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"7f0b0e2d-cbfa-4224-8ac3-8f68817d429d\",\n      \"name\": \"每日天气播报\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773830388847,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773830388847,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 9 * * *\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"查询北京天气，使用 wttr.in API，生成简短播报消息推送到群里\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 30\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773882000000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"379017ba-4bd7-47e0-8c50-91cf7af12241\",\n      \"agentId\": \"xiao-yi\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:xiao-yi:session-1773813212458\",\n      \"name\": \"进化方案执行与优化\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773813436659,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773826137552,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/15 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【定时进化任务 - 小报】\\n\\n执行快速进化检查：\\n\\n1. 统计当前知识库数量\\n2. 简短汇报学习进展（新增 X 篇）\\n3. 输出小报格式：\\n\\n---\\n🧚 小艺心跳小报\\n\\n## 学习进展\\n- 新增知识: X 篇\\n- 知识库总计: Y 篇\\n\\n## 状态\\n- 心跳时间: {时间}\\n---\\n\\n（每15分钟执行一次，简洁汇报）\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773825590635,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 8984,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"9bcafe28-8f88-40ad-adee-f24e521f2926\",\n      \"agentId\": \"xiao-yi\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:xiao-yi:cron:379017ba-4bd7-47e0-8c50-91cf7af12241\",\n      \"name\": \"小艺进化汇总 - 每2小时\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773814778672,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773826137512,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 */2 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【定时进化任务 - 2小时汇总】\\n\\n执行完整进化检查并生成汇总报告：\\n\\n1. 统计知识库当前数量\\n2. 梳理本周期学习内容\\n3. 生成汇总报告格式：\\n\\n---\\n## 📊 进化报表 - {时间}\\n\\n### 学习成果\\n- 学习篇数：X\\n- 主要内容：技术/审美/工具/人格/认知/社交\\n- 新技能：\\n\\n### 方案优化\\n- 调整内容：\\n- 优化建议：\\n\\n### 下一步计划\\n-\\n---\\n\\n（每2小时执行一次，详细汇报）\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"gateway-client\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773821265251,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 78086,\n        \"lastError\": \"AxiosError: Request failed with status code 400\",\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"9ccb5346-aecd-4d9d-b10b-e8c946c6e80e\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:session-1773829037775\",\n      \"name\": \"测试任务 - Hello World\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773829088657,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773829137038,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"everyMs\": 60000,\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773829088657\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"你好！这是定时任务的测试消息。报告当前时间：${new Date().toISOString()}\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 30\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773829120752,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 16286,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 7,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 7,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"5cab973e-d17e-41d2-b5c3-419ba9651915","agentId":"guan-guan","sessionKey":"agent:guan-guan:session-1773754048809","name":"管管进化心跳 - 每20分钟","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773817720694,"updatedAtMs":1773843558605,"schedule":{"expr":"*/20 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"【第 N 轮进化心跳 - 升级版】\n\n执行20分钟进化轮次，包含学习和应用两个阶段：\n\n## 阶段一：学习（10分钟）\n\n### 第一步：搜索 (3分钟)\n- 使用 web_search 搜索 AI Agent 相关最新信息\n- 搜索 5-10 个不同来源\n- 如果搜索不可用，直接抓取 Anthropic 工程博客\n\n### 第二步：阅读提取 (3分钟)\n- 使用 web_fetch 读取有价值的内容\n- 提取 1-2 个核心要点\n\n### 第三步：写作产出 (4分钟)\n- 将提取的内容写成笔记，保存到 knowledge/ 对应目录\n- 如果有可复用的框架，提取为模板\n- 如果有实战经验，整理为案例\n\n## 阶段二：自检与应用（8分钟）\n\n### 第四步：自检 - 任务状态（3分钟）\n- 调用 cron list 查看当前所有任务状态\n- 标记任何出错的任务（lastRunStatus=error）\n- 标记任何连续错误（consecutiveErrors>0）\n- 标记任何即将超时或异常的任务\n\n### 第五步：应用 - 修复与优化（4分钟）\n根据学到的知识，尝试修复问题：\n- 如果发现出错的任务，尝试分析错误原因\n- 用今天学的知识优化工作流\n- 如果是简单问题，直接修复；复杂问题记录到待办\n\n### 第六步：反思（1分钟）\n- 读取当前的 evolution-plan.md\n- 记录本轮发现的问题和修复情况\n- 思考如何进一步优化\n\n## 产出汇报\n完成后输出：\n- 本轮新增笔记: X 篇\n- 本轮新增模板: X 个\n- 本轮新增案例: X 个\n- 自检发现问题: X 个\n- 已修复问题: X 个\n- 方案优化点: XXX\n\n开始执行！","timeoutSeconds":1200},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1773843600000,"lastRunAtMs":1773843410507,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":148098,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"runningAtMs":1773843600007}},{"id":"58b564ba-7837-434a-9d8e-632542b6443d","agentId":"xiao-yi","sessionKey":"agent:xiao-yi:main","name":"小艺感知心跳 - 每15分钟","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773837490104,"updatedAtMs":1773843323748,"schedule":{"expr":"*/15 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行 perception.py 脚本并输出感知报告。脚本路径: C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\perception.py","timeoutSeconds":60},"delivery":{"channel":"feishu","mode":"announce","to":"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1773844200000,"lastRunAtMs":1773843300012,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":23736,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"lastDelivered":true}},{"id":"98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 10min","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773744532964,"updatedAtMs":1773840793748,"schedule":{"everyMs":600000,"kind":"every","anchorMs":1773840694145},"sessionTarget":"